    <string name="dummy_privacy_content">At Nuerocheck, we take your privacy seriously. This policy describes how we collect, use, and handle your medical data and personal information. All scans are processed securely using advanced AI models and are stored with industry-standard encryption.\n\n1. Data Collection: We collect only the data necessary for diagnostic purposes.\n2. Data Usage: Your data is used solely to provide analysis and historical records.\n3. Security: We implement rigorous security measures to protect against unauthorized access.</string>
    <string name="dummy_terms_content">Welcome to Nuerocheck. By using our application, you agree to the following terms and conditions:\n\n1. Medical Disclaimer: This app is a diagnostic aid and should not replace professional medical judgment.\n2. User Account: You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.\n3. Prohibited Use: You may not use the app for any illegal or unauthorized purpose.</string>
